data <- read_excel("Stats_Deidentified.xlsx")

data <- data %>%
  mutate(status = ifelse(`Vital status` == "Alive", 0, 1)) %>%
  mutate(time   = `Diagnosis to Last Status`) %>%
  mutate(treatment = `Treatment Intent`) %>%
  mutate(treatment = ifelse(treatment == "Definitive CRT", "CRT", "Trimodal")) %>%
  mutate(stage = ifelse(`Prognostic Stage` == "I"| `Prognostic Stage` == "III" | 
                          `Prognostic Stage` == "IIA"| `Prognostic Stage` == "IIB"| `Prognostic Stage` == "IIIB", "I-III", 
                               ifelse(`Prognostic Stage` == "IVA"| `Prognostic Stage` == "IVB", "IV", `Prognostic Stage`)))

Before applying propensity score matching

### fitting univariate model
library(survival)

# build survival model table
t1 <-
  coxph(Surv(time, status) ~ treatment + Sex + `Age at Diagnosis` + `RT Fractions Received` + `RT Dose Received` + `5-FU/Cisplatin` + stage + `Carbo/Taxol`, data) %>%
  tbl_regression(exponentiate = TRUE)

t2 <-
  coxph(Surv(time, status) ~ treatment, data) %>%
  tbl_regression(exponentiate = TRUE)

t3 <-
  coxph(Surv(time, status) ~ Sex, data) %>%
  tbl_regression(exponentiate = TRUE)

t4 <-
  coxph(Surv(time, status) ~  `Age at Diagnosis`, data) %>%
  tbl_regression(exponentiate = TRUE)

t5 <-
  coxph(Surv(time, status) ~ `RT Fractions Received`, data) %>%
  tbl_regression(exponentiate = TRUE)

t6 <-
  coxph(Surv(time, status) ~ `RT Dose Received`, data) %>%
  tbl_regression(exponentiate = TRUE)

t7 <-
  coxph(Surv(time, status) ~ `5-FU/Cisplatin`, data) %>%
  tbl_regression(exponentiate = TRUE)

t8 <-
  coxph(Surv(time, status) ~ stage, data) %>%
  tbl_regression(exponentiate = TRUE)

t9 <-
  coxph(Surv(time, status) ~ `Carbo/Taxol`, data) %>%
  tbl_regression(exponentiate = TRUE)

tbl_merge_ex1 <-
  tbl_merge(
    tbls = list(t1, t2, t3, t4, t5, t6, t7, t8, t9),
    tab_spanner = c("**Multivariate**", "**Univariate**",  "**Univariate**", "**Univariate**",  "**Univariate**", "**Univariate**",  "**Univariate**", "**Univariate**",  "**Univariate**")
  )

After applying propensity score matching

data <- data %>% 
  mutate(trt = ifelse(treatment == "Definitive CRT", 1, 0))

modT <- glm(trt ~ Sex + `Age at Diagnosis` + `RT Fractions Received` + `RT Dose Received` + `5-FU/Cisplatin` + stage + `Carbo/Taxol`, data = data, family = "binomial")
## Warning: glm.fit: algorithm did not converge
probT <- predict(modT, type = "response")
data$w <- 1/ifelse(data$trt == 1, probT, 1 - probT)


library(survival)

# build survival model table
t1 <-
  coxph(Surv(time, status) ~ treatment + Sex + `Age at Diagnosis` + `RT Fractions Received` + `RT Dose Received` + `5-FU/Cisplatin` + stage + `Carbo/Taxol`, data, method = "breslow", weights = w) %>%
  tbl_regression(exponentiate = TRUE)

Plots before applying propensity score matching

data <- data %>%
  mutate(time_yr = time / 365.25)

splots <- list()
fit <-  survfit(Surv(time_yr, status) ~ treatment, data = data)
splots[[1]] <- ggsurvplot(
    fit, data, 
    break.time.by = 1,
    xlim = c(0, 8),
    legend.labs = c("CRT", "Trimodality"),
    xlab = "Time (Years)",
    ylab = "Overall survival probability")


fit1 <-  survfit(Surv(time_yr, status) ~ treatment, data = data[data$stage == "I-III", ])
splots[[2]] <- ggsurvplot(
    fit1, data[data$stage == "I-III", ], 
    break.time.by = 1,
    xlim = c(0, 8),
    legend.labs = c("CRT", "Trimodality"),
    xlab = "Time (Years)",
    surv.plot.height = 2.5,
    ylab = "Overall survival probability")

fit2 <-  survfit(Surv(time_yr, status) ~ treatment, data = data[data$stage == "IV", ])
splots[[3]] <- ggsurvplot(
    fit2, data[data$stage == "IV", ], 
    break.time.by = 1,
    xlim = c(0, 8),
    legend.labs = c("CRT", "Trimodality"),
    xlab = "Time (Years)",
    surv.plot.height = 2.5,
    ylab = "Overall survival probability")

arrange_ggsurvplots(splots, print = TRUE,
  ncol = 2, nrow = 2 )

pdf("survivalplot_beforematching_trtintent.pdf", width = 10, height = 8)
arrange_ggsurvplots(splots, print = TRUE,
  ncol = 2, nrow = 2)
dev.off()

After applying propensity score matching

data <- data %>% 
  mutate(trt = ifelse(treatment == "Definitive CRT", 1, 0))

modT <- glm(trt ~ Sex + `Age at Diagnosis` + `RT Fractions Received` + `RT Dose Received` + `5-FU/Cisplatin` + stage + `Carbo/Taxol`, data = data, family = "binomial")
probT <- predict(modT, type = "response")
data$w <- 1/ifelse(data$trt == 1, probT, 1 - probT)


library(survival)

# build survival model table
t1 <-
  coxph(Surv(time, status) ~ treatment + Sex + `Age at Diagnosis` + `RT Fractions Received` + `RT Dose Received` + `5-FU/Cisplatin` + stage + `Carbo/Taxol`, data, method = "breslow", weights = w) %>%
  tbl_regression(exponentiate = TRUE)

t2 <-
  coxph(Surv(time, status) ~ treatment, data, method = "breslow", weights = w) %>%
  tbl_regression(exponentiate = TRUE)

t3 <-
  coxph(Surv(time, status) ~ Sex, data, method = "breslow", weights = w) %>%
  tbl_regression(exponentiate = TRUE)

t4 <-
  coxph(Surv(time, status) ~  `Age at Diagnosis`, data, method = "breslow", weights = w) %>%
  tbl_regression(exponentiate = TRUE)

t5 <-
  coxph(Surv(time, status) ~ `RT Fractions Received`, data, method = "breslow", weights = w) %>%
  tbl_regression(exponentiate = TRUE)

t6 <-
  coxph(Surv(time, status) ~ `RT Dose Received`, data, method = "breslow", weights = w) %>%
  tbl_regression(exponentiate = TRUE)

t7 <-
  coxph(Surv(time, status) ~ `5-FU/Cisplatin`, data, method = "breslow", weights = w) %>%
  tbl_regression(exponentiate = TRUE)

t8 <-
  coxph(Surv(time, status) ~ stage, data, method = "breslow", weights = w) %>%
  tbl_regression(exponentiate = TRUE)

t9 <-
  coxph(Surv(time, status) ~ `Carbo/Taxol`, data, method = "breslow", weights = w) %>%
  tbl_regression(exponentiate = TRUE)

tbl_merge_ex2 <-
  tbl_merge(
    tbls = list(t1, t2, t3, t4, t5, t6, t7, t8, t9),
    tab_spanner = c("**Multivariate**", "**Univariate**",  "**Univariate**", "**Univariate**",  "**Univariate**", "**Univariate**",  "**Univariate**", "**Univariate**",  "**Univariate**")
  )

Plots before applying propensity score matching

data <- data %>%
  mutate(time_yr = time / 365.25)

splots <- list()
fit <-  survfit(Surv(time_yr, status) ~ treatment, data = data)
splots[[1]] <- ggsurvplot(
    fit, data, 
    break.time.by = 1,
    xlim = c(0, 8),
    legend.labs = c("CRT", "Trimodality"),
    xlab = "Time (Years)",
    ylab = "Overall survival probability")


fit1 <-  survfit(Surv(time_yr, status) ~ treatment, data = data[data$stage == "I-III", ])
splots[[2]] <- ggsurvplot(
    fit1, data[data$stage == "I-III", ], 
    break.time.by = 1,
    xlim = c(0, 8),
    legend.labs = c("CRT", "Trimodality"),
    xlab = "Time (Years)",
    surv.plot.height = 2.5,
    ylab = "Overall survival probability")

fit2 <-  survfit(Surv(time_yr, status) ~ treatment, data = data[data$stage == "IV", ])
splots[[3]] <- ggsurvplot(
    fit2, data[data$stage == "IV", ], 
    break.time.by = 1,
    xlim = c(0, 8),
    legend.labs = c("CRT", "Trimodality"),
    xlab = "Time (Years)",
    surv.plot.height = 2.5,
    ylab = "Overall survival probability")

arrange_ggsurvplots(splots, print = TRUE,
  ncol = 2, nrow = 2 )

pdf("survivalplot_beforematching_trtrevised.pdf", width = 10, height = 8)
arrange_ggsurvplots(splots, print = TRUE,
  ncol = 2, nrow = 2)
dev.off()
